{"name":"Short Fuse","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Short Fuse</p>\n<p>You have a legendary temper. It&rsquo;s not exclusively aggravated by the options below, but choose two triggers that really get your goat.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Challenge</li>\n<li>Injustice</li>\n<li>Pain</li>\n<li>Confusion</li>\n<li>Insecurity</li>\n<li>Surprise</li>\n<li>_______________</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Whenever s omething makes you angry, mark 1 Fury. If i t&rsquo;s one of your triggers, mark 2 Fury.</p>","class":"The Berserker","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":0,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"starting","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"1an3hIjG536aYVum"}
{"name":"Rage","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Rage (CON)</p>\n<p>When y ou reach 3 Fury and you&rsquo;re not already raging, you enter a ferocious and terrible rage. Roll+CON.</p>\n<p>On a hit mark an additional fury and take +1 ongoing to all rolls you make with STR, DEX or CON.</p>\n<p>On a 7-9, your rage makes you reckless and short-sighted: whenever you deal damage while raging the GM will tell you what collateral damage you invoke.</p>\n<p>On a 6-, l ose 1 Fury i n addition to whatever the GM says.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>While raging, you have additional armor equal to your CON.</p>\n<p>Lose 1 Fury every time you deal damage. When you reach 0 Fury, your rage ends and you mark a debility of your choice.</p>","class":"The Berserker","rollType":"CON","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":0,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"starting","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"Oi9CkSbRlYfs8Zgs"}
{"name":"Can I Kick it?","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Can I Kick it?</p>\n<p>When you heedlessly power through a physical obstacle, roll+STR.</p>\n<p>On a hit take [[/r 1d6]] damage, mark 1 Fury, and the obstacle is destroyed.</p>\n<p>On a 7-9, take an additional [[/r 1d6]] damage or the GM puts you i n a spot, your choice.</p>","class":"The Berserker","rollType":"STR","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":0,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"starting","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"dQr297Szs9PvY1WR"}
{"name":"Improvised Weaponry","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Improvised Weaponry</p>\n<p>Even the most mundane of objects is a weapon in your capable hands.</p>\n<p>When you pick up an object not normally considered to be a weapon, the GM will tell you what tags it has while you wield it.</p>\n<p>When you d eal damage with an improvised weapon, roll [[/r 1d4]]. On any result other than a 1, i t breaks.</p>","class":"The Berserker","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":0,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"starting","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"KKU8X5VWkwn3o4IB"}
{"name":"Sunâ€™s Getting Real Low","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Sun&rsquo;s Getting Real Low</p>\n<p>When you spend time doing something that calms you down, lose 1 Fury.</p>\n<p>If anyone who has a bond with you h elps you, lose an additional Fury.</p>\n<p>If losing Fury this way ends your rage, you don&rsquo;t mark a debility.</p>","class":"The Berserker","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":0,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"starting","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"vcE5fyCJrJld2IgR"}
{"name":"Fierce Protector","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Fierce Protector</p>\n<p>While you Defend something or someone, whenever that which you protect takes damage or is otherwise hurt, you gain 1 Fury.</p>","class":"The Berserker","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":2,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"vTIEjJXDiQXX4QpI"}
{"name":"You Mad?","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>You Mad?</p>\n<p>When you goad an enemy into making a reckless, angry action, roll+CHA.</p>\n<p>On a hit they make a critical mistake in an effort to spite or smite you and you take +1 forward against them.</p>\n<p>On a 7-9, your cool tactics cool your blood, lose 1 Fury.</p>","class":"The Berserker","rollType":"CHA","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":2,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"L1A52f9CfZ04SEHg"}
{"name":"Mindless Killing Machine","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Mindless Killing Machine</p>\n<p>When you a re afflicted by fear, mind control, or enchanting magic, you may ignore the effect as l ong as you attack the closest enemy in sight.</p>\n<p>If you have no enemies i n sight, the GM chooses who you attack.</p>","class":"The Berserker","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":2,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"uYqvhbploHAQn9bV"}
{"name":"Iâ€™m The Juggernaut, Buddy","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>I&rsquo;m The Juggernaut, Buddy</p>\n<p>When you use Can I Kick It? while raging, you take +1 forward on a hit and take no damage on a 10+.</p>","class":"The Berserker","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":2,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"p7t2PU4G7qUvj1oU"}
{"name":"Red-Blooded","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Red-Blooded</p>\n<p>When you deal damage, you deal additional damage equal to your current Fury.</p>\n<p>This triggers before you lose Fury for dealing damage if you are raging.</p>","class":"The Berserker","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":2,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"eIDVMPS87kOCMseR"}
