{"name":"Ancestral Guardian","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Ancestral Guardian</p>\n<p>The spectre of an ancient warrior of your bloodline guards you i n your fury.</p>\n<p>While raging, you have +1 armor.</p>\n<p>When y ou command the guardian to protect an ally, you may transfer this bonus to them.</p>","class":"The Berserker","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":2,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"4tTM0BsjXlFwTPYh"}
{"name":"Animal Totem","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Animal Totem</p>\n<p>Choose an animal that you mimic when you rage.</p>\n<p>Work with the GM to write an animal move, as detailed i n the Druid playbook.</p>\n<p>Spend 1 Fury to make that move while raging.</p>","class":"The Berserker","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":2,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"kkdZeVHwmjbiMiuM"}
{"name":"Undying One","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Undying One</p>\n<p>You mark an additional Fury when you rage, even on a 6-, and you can spend all your fury while raging to heal [[/r 1d6]] for each fury spent.</p>","class":"The Berserker","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":2,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"J34NoTON0phPgwvw"}
